- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper mentions the efficiency factor GQR, which is necessary for standardless fission-track dating. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with photomicrographs and image processing techniques. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of skeletonization, which is a common algorithmic technique in computer science. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with visual data (photomicrographs) and image processing techniques.
